{"id":790975,"name":"K H A G E","username":"KHAGE","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/llllllll.co/khage/{size}/107026_2.png","created_at":"2026-04-24T07:29:52.593Z","cooked":"\u003cp\u003eI finally managed to get my hands on two more units, but unfortunately one of the Stem Players arrived with a broken fader near the control knob.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://llllllll.co/uploads/default/original/3X/d/b/db9dc96bb62c61afbfde755b85814d6d612e9ece.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://llllllll.co/uploads/default/db9dc96bb62c61afbfde755b85814d6d612e9ece\" title=\"Broken Stem fader\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://llllllll.co/uploads/default/optimized/3X/d/b/db9dc96bb62c61afbfde755b85814d6d612e9ece_2_374x500.jpeg\" alt=\"Broken Stem fader\" data-base62-sha1=\"vkOCBBWjGMyJ5AUFb6Q8oK8LQnA\" width=\"374\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://llllllll.co/uploads/default/optimized/3X/d/b/db9dc96bb62c61afbfde755b85814d6d612e9ece_2_374x500.jpeg, https://llllllll.co/uploads/default/optimized/3X/d/b/db9dc96bb62c61afbfde755b85814d6d612e9ece_2_561x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://llllllll.co/uploads/default/optimized/3X/d/b/db9dc96bb62c61afbfde755b85814d6d612e9ece_2_748x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"BBCED1\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse href=\"#far-image\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003cspan class=\"filename\"\u003eBroken Stem fader\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"informations\"\u003e1421×1895 158 KB\u003c/span\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse href=\"#discourse-expand\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://llllllll.co/images/emoji/apple/scream.png?v=15\" title=\":scream:\" class=\"emoji only-emoji\" alt=\":scream:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://llllllll.co/images/emoji/apple/sad_but_relieved_face.png?v=15\" title=\":sad_but_relieved_face:\" class=\"emoji only-emoji\" alt=\":sad_but_relieved_face:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://llllllll.co/images/emoji/apple/sob.png?v=15\" title=\":sob:\" class=\"emoji only-emoji\" alt=\":sob:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis actually makes me want to be extremely careful with my other Stem Players, as this plastic part seems particularly delicate and fragile to me.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDo you think there’s any way to replace this fader?\u003cbr\u003e\nI could try gluing the knob back on, but it’s so thin that I’m afraid the glue might run off to the side and jam the linear movement.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSince I know I can’t request a replacement for this unit, what would you do in my place?\u003cbr\u003e\nIs this third fader beyond repair?… Or do you think there might be a solution?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThank you very much for your time and your valuable advice. \u003cimg src=\"https://llllllll.co/images/emoji/apple/folded_hands/4.png?v=15\" title=\":folded_hands:t4:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":folded_hands:t4:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","post_number":863,"post_type":1,"posts_count":846,"updated_at":"2026-04-24T07:29:52.593Z","reply_count":3,"reply_to_post_number":691,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":2,"reads":271,"readers_count":270,"score":153.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":66795,"topic_slug":"te-stem-player","display_username":"K H A G E","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":12340,"username":"KHAGE","name":"K H A G E","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/llllllll.co/khage/{size}/107026_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"I finally managed to get my hands on two more units, but unfortunately one of the Stem Players arrived with a broken fader near the control knob.\n\n![Broken Stem fader|374x500](upload://vkOCBBWjGMyJ5AUFb6Q8oK8LQnA.jpeg)\n\n😱😥😭\n\nThis actually makes me want to be extremely careful with my other Stem Players, as this plastic part seems particularly delicate and fragile to me.\n\nDo you think there’s any way to replace this fader?\nI could try gluing the knob back on, but it’s so thin that I’m afraid the glue might run off to the side and jam the linear movement.\n\nSince I know I can’t request a replacement for this unit, what would you do in my place?\nIs this third fader beyond repair?… Or do you think there might be a solution?\n\nThank you very much for your time and your valuable advice. 🙏🏽","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"count":5}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":12340,"hidden":false,"trust_level":3,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/te-stem-player/66795/863","can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}